# Database Patterns

- All DB access via repositories in `packages/infra/supabase/`
- Upsert key: `jira_key` (BB-DATA-01)
- Migrations in `supabase/migrations/` — never modify applied migrations
- Specify columns; no `SELECT *` in production
- JSON columns: consistent `JSON.stringify` encoding

No raw SQL in route handlers or domain layer.
